23-the-food-drive-p4-s3","ord":2,"text":"Jun was surprised because Mina had brought more than he had.","translation_ko":"준은 미나가 자기보다 더 많이 가져왔다는 것에 놀랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-123-the-food-drive/audio/p4-s3.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"was","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":340,"endMs":580},{"word":"surprised","charStart":8,"charEnd":17,"startMs":580,"endMs":1180},{"word":"because","charStart":18,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1860},{"word":"Mina","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2120},{"word":"had","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2360},{"word":"brought","charStart":35,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2580},{"word":"more","charStart":43,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2840},{"word":"than","charStart":48,"charEnd":52,"startMs":2840,"endMs":3020},{"word":"he","charStart":53,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3020,"endMs":3220},{"word":"had","charStart":56,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3220,"endMs":3500}]}]},{"id":"daily-123-the-food-drive-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-123-the-food-drive/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-123-the-food-drive-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"Together, they placed their cans carefully into the big box.","translation_ko":"둘이 함께 통조림을 조심스럽게 큰 상자 안에 담았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-123-the-food-drive/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Together","charStart":0,"charEnd":8,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"they","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":680,"endMs":1240},{"word":"placed","charStart":15,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1460},{"word":"their","charStart":22,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1700},{"word":"cans","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2020},{"word":"carefully","charStart":33,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2580},{"word":"into","charStart":43,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2580,"endMs":3100},{"word":"the","charStart":48,"charEnd":51,"startMs":3100,"endMs":3260},{"word":"big","charStart":52,"char